NAME
    Net::Nomad - Nomad REST API client.

SYNOPSIS
DESCRIPTION
    Net::Nomad is object oriented interface to the Nomad REST API
    <https://www.nomadproject.io/api/index.html>.

ACCESSORS
  host
    Defaults to 127.0.0.1

  port
    Default 4646.

  name
    Username for authentication

  password
    Authentication credentials

  cacert
    Path to cacert

  ssl
    To enable set to 1

  api_version
    defaults to /v1

  api_path
    The full api path. Defaults to http://127.0.0.1:4646/v1

PUBLIC METHODS
  agent
    See Net::Nomad::Agent

        # query self
        $nomad->agent()->self;

        # check agent health
        $nomad->agent()->health;

